Interface DamagableInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
Asteroid, GameCharacter, PlayerCharacter
public interface DamagableInterface
An interface for any actor that can be damaged. Characters, asteroids, and rockets are examples.

    boolean hurtActor​(Actor causingActor, float damageQuantity)
    Damage the actor
